pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `3a56677` to `08ac2b1`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `3a56677` to `08ac2b1`.
Commits
  • 08ac2b1 liobqs 0.6.0-rc3
  • 70eae32 Quick fix to Kyber768-90s NIST level (#1014)
  • 2e7f657 Add astyle to Ubuntu install instructions [skip ci]
  • f8e339d liboqs 0.6.0 RC2
  • bd23977 tests/constant_time: update SIKE suppression files [skip ci] (#1009)
  • 8d7e8f5 Consistent type in KEM decaps API (#1004) (#1005)
  • 63ffa98 Integrated sike compressed elligator fix. (#1008)
  • 35489ee ARM64 via CCI machine (#1010)
  • See full diff in compare view
